data.description: Now price reduced..!!  Traditional living at it's Best, & enjoy the View..!  Low overhead with solar pmt. of $69/mo, and $25 mo electric bills. Slump block construction for low maintenance, and home is well cared for. This 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Home, (currently 3rd BR is opened & being used as Den,) Has Split Floorplan with large Living-Family Room .  To add to the charm there is a 16x20 she Shed for craft-quilting, etc and a 12x12 He Shed/workshop in all fenced back yard under huge shade canopy. Large front porch with view, & 2 separate rear patios. Plenty of room to park large RV alongside garage.  Roof was Replaced in 2022 and oversized garage has Mini split A/C cooling, with plenty of built-in storage. House A/C fairly new in good condition. Very nice simple landscaping is well manicured.
